<varlistentry id="options.DisableKDEGlobalsTheming">
	<term>DisableKDEGlobalsTheming</term>
	<listitem>
		<para>If set will prevent AfterStep from updating private kdeglobals file when colorscheme is changed.
		kdeglobals needs to be updated in order to set colors for KDE apps to match that of the selected colorscheme.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
